Class ElapsedTime

java.lang.Object
gw.pl.logging.ElapsedTime
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoggingKeyValue
public class ElapsedTime extends Object implements LoggingKeyValue
Key value pair for logging elapsed time. elapsedTimeMs is the key, the value is in milliseconds.
